name: Material
tagline: An HTML5 responsive template incorporating Google's Material Design Standards along with Jekyll -- Work in Progress --
body:
### Welcome to Material - A Material Design Study.
Ok. I've forked naveenshaji former repository so I can study and understand what he did with his Material Design free theme. This theme isn't made by me as you can noticed while navigating throuhg my github account.

But you could take a look at some projects of mine, located at: http://www.github.com/falexvidal. There's one work in progress and another consists on my personal website, which I believe needs some improvements. Any help here is welcome.

Keep in touch!
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
